extDescription.message: Generate unit tests from AtCoder's problem page.

tutorialBody.message:
1. Open AtCoder problem page
  2. Click on the toolbar
  3. Paste into editor

releaseNoteBody.message:
AtCoder Unit Test is new!

  • Test code templates can now be changed.
  • The method of copying tests has been changed.
    (On the AtCoder problem page, click on the toolbar)
  • Python
    • You can now submit your work with the test code included.( Example )
  • Java, Kotlin
    • The test library has been changed to his JUnit5.

warning_template.message: Overwrite what you have already entered.

write_method.message: Write {{ METHOD }} where you want to insert the test method.

write_name.message: Write {{ NAME }} where you want to insert the test mthod name.

write_input.message: Write {{ INPUT }} where you want to insert the input example.

write_output.message: Write {{ OUTPUT }} where you want to insert the output example
